            <head xml:id="bHY6yh-d34168-Hd1e108">Rubrica 8</head>
            <head xml:id="bHY6yh-d34168-Hd1e111" type="question-title">De rixis et scandalis</head>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d34168-d1e114">
               
       De rixis et scandalis Rubrica. 8.
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d34168-d1e119">
               <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d34168-Rd1e121">SAlomon in prouerb. c. 10</ref>
      
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d34168-Qd1e125">Odium suscitat
        rixas.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d34168-d1e131">
            <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d34168-Rd1e129">15. c.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d34168-Qd1e133">Uir iracundus prouocat
        rixas: qui patiens est mitigatur susci
        tatas.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d34168-d1e142">
            <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d34168-Rd1e138">18. c.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d34168-Qd1e144">Labia stulti immiscent se rixis:
        et os eius iurgia prouocat.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d34168-d1e150">
               
              <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d34168-Rd1e146">Iesus filius sirach in eccl. c. 8.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d34168-Qd1e154">Cum iracundo
        non facies rixam.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d34168-d1e160">
            <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d34168-Rd1e154">27.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d34168-Qd1e162">Effusio sanguinis in
        rixam superborum.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d34168-d1e168">
               
              <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d34168-Rd1e162">Mattheus in euangel. c. 18.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d34168-Qd1e172">Uhe mundo a
        scandalis. Necesse est vt veniant scandala:
        veruntamen vhe homini per quem scandalum venit.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d34168-d1e180">
               
              <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d34168-Rd1e170">Cato. c. 2.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d34168-Qd1e184">Rumores fuge: ne incipias no
        uus auctor haberi.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d34168-d1e190">
               
              <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d34168-Rd1e178">Isidorus solilo. li. 2. et fi. c. 26</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d34168-Qd1e194">Fuge rixam</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d34168-d1e199">
               
              <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d34168-Rd1e187">Iacobus beneuentanus. c. 5.</ref>
        <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d34168-Qd1e203">Lingua odium parit: et faciet tibi litem.
        Effreni lingua: surgere bella solent.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d34168-d1e211">
               
              <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d34168-Rd1e195">Prouerb. vulgar.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d34168-Qd1e215">Del can grintoso: eno<!--116.xml-->
        <cb ed="#V" n="b"/>
                  forroso guai la pelle.</quote>
            </p>
         </div>
